@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hosobc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (tmp * wp.exp((v0 + 0.72 / v1 + 0.72)))
    v2 = (((v2 + 0.05 - tmp + 0.66) / wp.sin(v2 + 0.17)) + wp.cos(v0))
    v2 = wp.exp((0.41 - v2))
    tmp = v1
    v1 = wp.exp(1.00)
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.59) * wp.sin(v2 + 0.12)) - tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
